trans-unit.source: Represents a workflow queue.
trans-unit.target: 워크플로 큐를 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] Workflow queues are used to pass messages between a host or host services and activities in a workflow.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]워크플로 큐는 메시지를 전달 하는 호스트 또는 호스트 서비스 및 워크플로의 활동 간에 사용 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: Any activity can create a WorkflowQueue by calling <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService.CreateWorkflowQueue%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, and a host, a service, or another activity can call <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Enqueue%2A> to add an item to that WorkflowQueue.
trans-unit.target: 모든 활동이 호출 하 여 한 WorkflowQueue를 만들 수 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService.CreateWorkflowQueue%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, 호스트, 서비스 또는 다른 작업을 호출할 수 있습니다 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Enqueue%2A>해당 WorkflowQueue에 항목을 추가 하려면.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Enqueue%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService.CreateWorkflowQueue%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You can subscribe to the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.QueueItemAvailable> event to be notified when an item arrives on the WorkflowQueue.
trans-unit.target: 구독할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.QueueItemAvailable>이벤트 항목 WorkflowQueue에 도착 될 때 알림을 받을 수 있습니다.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.QueueItemAvailable>

trans-unit.source: You can use <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Peek%2A> to examine an item at the beginning of the WorkflowQueue and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Dequeue%2A> to remove an item from the WorkflowQueue.
trans-unit.target: 사용할 수 있습니다 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Peek%2A>WorkflowQueue의 시작 부분에 있는 항목을 검사 하 고 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Dequeue%2A>WorkflowQueue에서 항목을 제거 하려면.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Dequeue%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.Peek%2A>

trans-unit.source: Each WorkflowQueue is associated with a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService> that you can use to perform other management operations on the WorkflowQueue, such as deleting the queue.
trans-unit.target: 각 WorkflowQueue과 연관 된 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService>큐를 삭제 하는 등 WorkflowQueue의 다른 관리 작업을 수행 하는 데 사용할 수 있는.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.QueuingService%2A> exposes the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService> associated with this WorkflowQueue.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.QueuingService%2A>노출 된 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService>이 WorkflowQueue와 관련 된.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueuingService></xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue.QueuingService%2A>

trans-unit.source: The event handler may execute on a non-workflow thread so access to any shared workflow object, for example, any <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject>, must be protected.
